### ============================================================
### BuildSmart IAM Service - API Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:8082
### ============================================================
### NOTE: IAM requires MySQL running on localhost:3306
###       Database: buildsmart_iam
###       Ensure Eureka Server is running on port 8761

### =====================
### HEALTH CHECK
### =====================

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### 2. Swagger UI (open in browser)
# http://localhost:8082/swagger-ui.html


### =====================
### AUTH - SIGNUP
### =====================

