### =====================
### AUTH - LOGIN
### =====================

### 12. Login - Admin (NOTE: New users start as PENDING_VERIFICATION.
###    You need to first approve the admin user via DB or use a pre-seeded admin)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@buildsmart.com",
  "password": "Admin123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.token);
    client.log("Admin Token: " + response.body.token);
%}

### 13. Login - Project Manager (after admin approves)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rajesh.kumar@buildsmart.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("pm_token", response.body.token);
    client.log("PM Token: " + response.body.token);
%}

### 14. Login - Site Engineer (after admin approves)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "anitha.sharma@buildsmart.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("se_token", response.body.token);
%}

### 15. Login - Invalid Credentials (should fail 401)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rajesh.kumar@buildsmart.com",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 16. Login - Non-existent User (should fail 401)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nobody@buildsmart.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}


### =====================
### USER PROFILE (JWT Required)
### Replace {{admin_token}}, {{pm_token}}, {{se_token}} with actual JWT tokens from login
### =====================

### 17. Get Current User Profile (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8082/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 18. Get Current User Profile (PM)
GET http://localhost:8082/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{pm_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 19. Get Current User Profile (SE)
GET http://localhost:8082/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{se_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 20. Update User Profile
PUT http://localhost:8082/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{pm_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rajesh Kumar Updated",
  "phone": "9876540000"
}

### 21. Check Role - PM checking PROJECT_MANAGER role
GET http://localhost:8082/users/check-role/PROJECT_MANAGER
Authorization: Bearer {{pm_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 22. Check Role - PM checking ADMIN role (should return hasRole: false)
GET http://localhost:8082/users/check-role/ADMIN
Authorization: Bearer {{pm_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 23. Check Role - Invalid Role (should fail 400)
GET http://localhost:8082/users/check-role/INVALID_ROLE
Authorization: Bearer {{pm_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 24. Profile without token (should fail 401)
GET http://localhost:8082/users/profile
Accept: application/json


### =====================
### ADMIN ENDPOINTS (Admin JWT Required)
### =====================

### 25. Get Pending Users (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8082/admin/pending-users
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 26. Approve User (replace USER_ID with actual pending user ID)
POST http://localhost:8082/admin/approve-user/PM001
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 27. Approve Site Engineer
POST http://localhost:8082/admin/approve-user/SE001
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 28. Approve Safety Officer
POST http://localhost:8082/admin/approve-user/SO001
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 29. Approve Vendor
POST http://localhost:8082/admin/approve-user/VN001
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 30. Approve Finance Officer
POST http://localhost:8082/admin/approve-user/FN001
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 31. Reject User (replace USER_ID)
POST http://localhost:8082/admin/reject-user/SOME_USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 32. Get All Users (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8082/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 33. Get All Users with Pagination
GET http://localhost:8082/admin/users?page=0&size=5&sortBy=createdAt&sortDir=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 34. Get User by ID (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8082/admin/users/PM001
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 35. Update User (Admin)
PUT http://localhost:8082/admin/users/SE001
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Anitha Sharma Updated",
  "phone": "9876543211",
  "role": "SITE_ENGINEER",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 36. Get Users by Role (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8082/admin/users/role/PROJECT_MANAGER
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 37. Get Users by Role - VENDOR (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8082/admin/users/role/VENDOR
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 38. Get Audit Logs (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8082/admin/audit-logs?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 39. Get Audit Logs for User (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8082/admin/audit-logs/user/PM001
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 40. Admin endpoint with non-admin token (should fail 403)
GET http://localhost:8082/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{pm_token}}
Accept: application/json


### =====================
### PASSWORD RESET
### =====================

### 41. Forgot Password
POST http://localhost:8082/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rajesh.kumar@buildsmart.com"
}

### 42. Reset Password (replace TOKEN with actual reset token from email)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "REPLACE_WITH_RESET_TOKEN",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123"
}

### 43. Validate Reset Token
GET http://localhost:8082/api/auth/validate-reset-token/REPLACE_WITH_RESET_TOKEN
Accept: application/json


### =====================
### LOGOUT
### =====================

### 44. Logout (invalidate token)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{se_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 45. Try using logged-out token (should fail 401)
GET http://localhost:8082/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{se_token}}
Accept: application/json


### =====================
### DELETE USER (Admin)
### =====================

### 46. Delete User (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:8082/admin/users/VN002
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 47. Verify Deletion
GET http://localhost:8082/admin/users/VN002
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json
